649b2529fbf0"],

Cell["\<\
SetOffDiagonalElementsToZero::usage=
\t\"SetOffDiagonalElementsToZero[mat,func] sets off-diagonal elements of the \
square matrix mat to zero, in the case that func[r,c] yields True, where r \
and c are the row and column indices. The diagonal elements are left \
untouched.\\n
\tSetOffDiagonalElementsToZero[mat] sets all off-diagonal elements to \
zero.\";
\t\
\>", "Input",
 PageWidth:>WindowWidth,
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.409664233707582*^9, 3.409664245245743*^9}, {
  3.430452523455375*^9, 3.430452632283009*^9}, {3.430452759367801*^9, 
